Package org.maxicp.cp.examples

Class DialARide.DialARideSolution

java.lang.Object
org.maxicp.cp.examples.DialARide.DialARideSolution
Enclosing class:
DialARide
public static class DialARide.DialARideSolution extends Object
A solution. To create one, first do new DialARideSolution, then add, for each vehicle, in order, the pickup/drops with addStop(vehicleIdx, rideIdx, isPickup), where vehicleIdx is an integer beginning at 0 and ending at nVehicles - 1, rideIdx is the id of the ride you (partly) fullfill with this stop (from 0 to pickupRideStops.size()-1) and isPickup a boolean indicate if you are beginning or ending the ride. Do not add the last stop to the depot, it is implicit.

You can check the validity of your solution with compute(), which returns the total distance, and raises an exception if something is invalid.

DO NOT MODIFY THIS CLASS.
